title: Outback Jack
overview: Outback Jack creates the ultimate test of love as 12 city women vie for the affections of a rugged Australian adventurer, Outback Jack. What the women don't realize, until it's too late, is that they must make a leap of faith by parachuting into the middle of Australia's expansive Outback wilderness. After making it to the ground, they are shocked to discover the potential man of their dreams is not living a life of luxury, but roughing it in one of the world's most unforgiving terrains. Over the course of eight episodes, the women will be put to the test, to see which one of them has the stamina to make it in the Outback and win the affection of their handsome hero.
